
user writes something on the text box and presses the button labeled "Save"

spa.js prevents the redirect by preventing default behaviour
spa.js stores the value of the textbox and the timestamp
spa.js redraws the list withe the inclusion of the new message
spa.js sends the contents of the message, converted to JSON, to the server with a POST request
browser->server: POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa
